d":"Sun Apr 10 2022 08:30:07 GMT+0000 (UTC)","nativeAd":false,"taxonomy":{"primaryVertical":{"name":"News","taxonomyType":"vertical"},"commerce":[]},"source":null,"authors":[{"authorType":"author","featuredAuthor":{"isFeaturedAuthor":false},"person":{"jobTitle":[],"name":"Scott Wong","primaryImage":{"url":{"primary":"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/newscms/2022_08/3536979/screen_shot_2022-02-24_at_12-15-16_am.png"}},"url":{"primary":"https://www.nbcnews.com/author/scott-wong-ncpn1288785"}}}]},"computedValues":{"teaseImage":{"url":{"primary":"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/rockcms/2022-04/220408-kevin-mccarthy-2019-ac-525p-a0d145.jpg"},"imageUrl":{"aims":"https://media1.s-nbcnews.com/i/rockcms/2022-04/40104/220408-kevin-mccarthy-2019-ac-525p-a0d145_cbb299ac0763a30bef259bf0f13dea42f9c92ef9.jpg","cloudinary":"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/rockcms/2022-04/220408-kevin-mccarthy-2019-ac-525p-a0d145.jpg","telemundo":null},"publisher":{"name":"nbcnews"},"source":{"name":"Getty Images file"},"authors":[{"name":"Win McNamee"}],"altText":"House Minority Leader Kevin McCarthy Holds Weekly Press Conference","caption":"House Minority Leader Kevin McCarthy, R-Calif., answers questions during a press conference at the U.S. Capitol on July 11, 2019.","height":1667,"width":2500},"alternateTeaseImages":[{"aspectRatio":"ASPECT_2X1","image":{"url":{"primary":"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/rockcms/2022-04/220408-kevin-mccarthy-2019-ac-525p-a0d145.jpg"},"source":{"name":"Getty Images file"},"authors":[{"name":"Win McNamee"}],"altText":"House Minority Leader Kevin McCarthy Holds Weekly Press Conference","caption":"House Minority Leader Kevin McCarthy, R-Calif., answers questions during a press conference at the U.S. Capitol on July 11, 2019.","height":1667,"width":2500}},{"aspectRatio":"ASPECT_1X1","image":{"url":{"primary":"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/rockcms/2022-04/220408-kevin-mccarthy-2019-ac-525p-a0d145.jpg"},"source":{"name":"Getty Images file"},"authors":[{"name":"Win McNamee"}],"altText":"House Minority Leader Kevin McCarthy Holds Weekly Press Conference","caption":"House Minority Leader Kevin McCarthy, R-Calif., answers questions during a press conference at the U.S. Capitol on July 11, 2019.","height":1667,"width":2500}}],"headline":"McCarthy's Jan. 6 committee gamble faces big test this spring","flag":null,"dek":"As the panel prepares to hold televised hearings, Kevin McCarthy's decision to boycott the committee could give Democrats a stronger hand as Republicans watch from the sidelines.","unibrow":{"logo":null,"taxonomyPath":"nbcnews/section/politics/congress","text":"Congress","url":{"primary":"https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress"}},"url":"https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/mccarthys-jan-6-committee-gamble-faces-big-test-spring-rcna23681"},"metadata":{},"related":[]},{"type":"liveBlog","autofilled":true,"id":"rcna23749","item":{"id":"rcna23749","breakingNews":false,"datePublished":"Mon Apr 11 2022 09:30:29 GMT+0000 (UTC)","dateModified":"Mon Apr 11 2022 09:30:29 GMT+0000 (UTC)","dateCreated":"Sun Apr 10 2022 08:02:19 GMT+0000 (Coordinated Universal Time)","nativeAd":false,"cards":[{"id":"rcrd459","authors":[{"bio":[{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"Dennis Romero is a breaking news reporter for NBC News Digital.&nbsp;"}],"id":"ncpn856406","email":"dennis.romero@nbcuni.com","jobTitle":[],"name":"Dennis Romero","primaryImage":{"altText":"Image: Dennis Romero","height":1500,"url":{"primary":"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/newscms/2020_03/3184066/dennis-romero-circle-byline-template.jpg"},"width":1500},"publisher":{"name":"nbcnews","subType":null,"type":"organization"},"socialMediaProfiles":{"email":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":"@drjournalist","pinterest":null,"twitter":"@dennisjromero","youtube":null},"subType":null,"type":"person","url":null,"worksFor":null}],"cardType":"TEXT","isHeadlineHidden":false,"content":{"markupAndEmbeds":[{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"Former President Donald Trump made clear \u003ca href=\"https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/meet-the-press/romney-trump-has-blind-spot-russia-face-hacking-invasion-n1251846\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ehis policy on Russia:\u003c/a\u003e Friendship is better than war. It's a reasonable concept, but more and more Americans don't buy it now that they've seen the devastation in Ukraine."},{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"In fact, without Trump in office, with \u003ca href=\"https://www.dni.gov/files/ODNI/documents/assessments/ICA-declass-16MAR21.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eRussia meddling in a second presidential election\u003c/a\u003e and with the daily imagery of Ukraine's manifest demolition, U.S. views have shifted dramatically: Seven in 10 Americans see the country as an enemy, compared with 4 in 10 in January, the \u003ca href=\"https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2022/04/06/seven-in-ten-americans-now-see-russia-as-an-enemy/?utm_source=Pew+Research+Center\u0026utm_campaign=a1f49c9d20-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2022_04_07_08_44\u0026utm_medium=email\u0026utm_term=0_3e953b9b70-a1f49c9d20-400042593\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ePew Research Center\u003c/a\u003e said in an email blast over the weekend about its latest polling data."},{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"But the real mind-blower here is that Republicans and Democrats agree to nearly within the \u003ca href=\"https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2022/04/06/russia-nato-ukraine-march-2022-methodology/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e+-2.3 percentage-point margin of error.\u003c/a\u003e About 72 percent of Democrats and 69 percent of Republicans now describe Russia as an enemy."},{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"Republicans had the biggest change of heart, with the proportion of GOP adults who have very unfavorable views of Russia doubling to 67 percent since 2020, Pew said."},{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"The highest proportion of American adults since Pew began measuring attitudes on Russia in 2008 now believes Russia is a major threat to the nation: 65 percent."}],"text":["Former President Donald Trump made clear his policy on Russia: Friendship is better than war. It's a reasonable concept, but more and more Americans don't buy it now that they've seen the devastation in Ukraine.","In fact, without Trump in office, with Russia meddling in a second presidential election and with the daily imagery of Ukraine's manifest demolition, U.S. views have shifted dramatically: Seven in 10 Americans see the country as an enemy, compared with 4 in 10 in January, the Pew Research Center said in an email blast over the weekend about its latest polling data.","But the real mind-blower here is that Republicans and Democrats agree to nearly within the +-2.3 percentage-point margin of error. About 72 percent of Democrats and 69 percent of Republicans now describe Russia as an enemy.","Republicans had the biggest change of heart, with the proportion of GOP adults who have very unfavorable views of Russia doubling to 67 percent since 2020, Pew said.","The highest proportion of American adults since Pew began measuring attitudes on Russia in 2008 now believes Russia is a major threat to the nation: 65 percent."]},"cardData":{"graphics":[]},"date":{"createdAt":"2022-04-11T04:25:11.685Z","publishedAt":"2022-04-11T04:25:11.685Z","modifiedAt":"2022-04-11T04:32:14.031Z"},"description":{"primary":"Former President Donald Trump made clear his policy on Russia: Friendship is better than war.","seo":"Former President Donald Trump made clear his policy on Russia: Friendship is better than war.","social":"More Americans view Russia as an enemy since the invasion"},"headline":{"primary":"More Americans view Russia as an enemy since the invasion","seo":"More Americans view Russia as an enemy since the invasion","social":"More Americans view Russia as an enemy since the invasion"},"primaryImage":null,"taxonomy":{"primaryChannel":{"id":"rctx38","path":"nbcnews/channel/nebula-blog-rcna23749","taxonomyType":"channel"},"primaryVertical":{"dateCreated":"Thu Sep 16 2021 03:51:57 GMT+0000 (UTC)","dateModified":"Thu Sep 16 2021 03:51:57 GMT+0000 (UTC)","description":{"primary":null},"id":"nctx20366","isCurated":null,"name":"News","path":"nbcnews/vertical/news","pageRoute":null,"slug":"news","type":"taxonomy","taxonomyType":"vertical","url":{"primary":null}}},"url":{"primary":"https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/live-blog/russia-ukraine-war-live-updates-kremlin-targeting-europe-zelenskyy-say-rcna23749#rcrd459"}},{"id":"rcrd458","authors":[{"bio":[{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"Dennis Romero is a breaking news reporter for NBC News Digital.&nbsp;"}],"id":"ncpn856406","email":"dennis.romero@nbcuni.com","jobTitle":[],"name":"Dennis Romero","primaryImage":{"altText":"Image: Dennis Romero","height":1500,"url":{"primary":"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/newscms/2020_03/3184066/dennis-romero-circle-byline-template.jpg"},"width":1500},"publisher":{"name":"nbcnews","subType":null,"type":"organization"},"socialMediaProfiles":{"email":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":"@drjournalist","pinterest":null,"twitter":"@dennisjromero","youtube":null},"subType":null,"type":"person","url":null,"worksFor":null}],"cardType":"TEXT","isHeadlineHidden":false,"content":{"markupAndEmbeds":[{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"The British defense ministry said Sunday that evidence of war crimes by Russian troops continued to mount as the invaders' retreat pulled the covers off new scenes of carnage."},{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"The ministry, citing intelligence, said the latest evidence was uncovered in northern Ukraine and that it includes the reported discovery of a mass grave containing the bodies of civilians near Burzova."},{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"NBC News has been unable to confirm the report with the U.S. Defense Department or Ukrainian officials."},{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"The U.K. ministry added that allegations of sex crimes by Russian troops have persisted as the forces appeared to ebb in the north."}],"text":["The British defense ministry said Sunday that evidence of war crimes by Russian troops continued to mount as the invaders' retreat pulled the covers off new scenes of carnage.","The ministry, citing intelligence, said the latest evidence was uncovered in northern Ukraine and that it includes the reported discovery of a mass grave containing the bodies of civilians near Burzova.","NBC News has been unable to confirm the report with the U.S. Defense Department or Ukrainian officials.","The U.K. ministry added that allegations of sex crimes by Russian troops have persisted as the forces appeared to ebb in the north."]},"cardData":{"graphics":[]},"date":{"createdAt":"2022-04-11T00:38:31.015Z","publishedAt":"2022-04-11T00:38:31.015Z","modifiedAt":"2022-04-11T05:45:09.797Z"},"description":{"primary":"The British defense ministry said Sunday that evidence of war crimes by Russian troops continued to mount as the invaders' retreat pulled the covers off new","seo":"The British defense ministry said Sunday that evidence of war crimes by Russian troops continued to mount as the invaders' retreat pulled the covers off new","social":"U.K. defense ministry: Evidence of war crimes continues to mount"},"headline":{"primary":"U.K. defense ministry: Evidence of war crimes continues to mount","seo":"U.K. defense ministry: Evidence of war crimes continues to mount","social":"U.K. defense ministry: Evidence of war crimes continues to mount"},"primaryImage":null,"taxonomy":{"primaryChannel":{"id":"rctx38","path":"nbcnews/channel/nebula-blog-rcna23749","taxonomyType":"channel"},"primaryVertical":{"dateCreated":"Thu Sep 16 2021 03:51:57 GMT+0000 (UTC)","dateModified":"Thu Sep 16 2021 03:51:57 GMT+0000 (UTC)","description":{"primary":null},"id":"nctx20366","isCurated":null,"name":"News","path":"nbcnews/vertical/news","pageRoute":null,"slug":"news","type":"taxonomy","taxonomyType":"vertical","url":{"primary":null}}},"url":{"primary":"https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/live-blog/russia-ukraine-war-live-updates-kremlin-targeting-europe-zelenskyy-say-rcna23749#rcrd458"}},{"id":"rcrd456","authors":[{"bio":[],"id":"ncpn1293923","email":"eric.hinton@nbcuni.com","jobTitle":[],"name":"Eric Hinton","primaryImage":null,"publisher":{"name":"nbcnews","subType":null,"type":"organization"},"socialMediaProfiles":{"email":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null,"pinterest":null,"twitter":null,"youtube":null},"subType":null,"type":"person","url":null,"worksFor":null}],"cardType":"TEXT","isHeadlineHidden":false,"content":{"markupAndEmbeds":[{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy accused the Russian military of lying and cowardliness in his latest official video post Sunday as he proposed and promoted new sanctions against Russia."},{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"“The Russian military are lying so much that even after six weeks of the war they claim that they did not hit a single civilian target. You know why? Because it is cowardliness. Total. Of everyone, from top to bottom,” he said.&nbsp;"},{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"“They captured Crimea and blamed us. They destroyed normal life in Donbas, and we are somehow to blame. They shot down the Malaysia Airlines Boeing, and we are somehow to blame. For eight years, they have been killing the people, children on our land. And we are somehow to blame,” Zelenskyy added."},{"type":"markup","element":"p","html":"Zelenskyy said that when people lack the courage to admit their mistakes, apologize, adapt to reality and learn, they become \"monsters.\" \"And when the world ignores it, the monsters decide that the world must adapt to them. Ukraine will stop all this. Nothing will help Russian cowardice. The day will come when they will have to admit everything, admit the truth.”"}],"text":["Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy accused the Russian military of lying and cowardliness in his latest official video post Sunday as he proposed and promoted new sanctions against Russia.","“The Russian military are lying so much that even after six weeks of the war they claim that they did not hit a single civilian target. You know why? Because it is cowardliness. Total. Of everyone, from top to bottom,” he said.&nbsp;","“They captured Crimea and blamed us. They destroyed normal life in Donbas, and we are somehow to blame. They shot down the Malaysia Airlines Boeing, and we are somehow to blame. For eight years, they have been killing the people, children on our land. And we are somehow to blame,” Zelenskyy added.","Zelenskyy said that when people lack the courage to admit their mistakes, apologize, adapt to reality and learn, they become \"monsters.\" \"And when the world ignores it, the monsters decide that the world must adapt to them. Ukraine will stop all this. Nothing will help Russian cowardice. The day will come when they will have to admit everything, admit the truth.”"]},"cardData":{"graphics":[]},"date":{"createdAt":"2022-04-10T20:47:25.198Z","publishedAt":"2022-04-10T20:47:25.198Z","modifiedAt":"2022-04-11T04:10:15.579Z"},"description":{"primary":"Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy accused the Russian military of lying and cowardliness in his latest official video post Sunday as he proposed and","seo":"Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy accused the Russian military of lying and cowardliness in his latest official video post Sunday as he proposed and","social":"Zelenskyy accuses Russia of 'cowardliness' in latest video address"},"headline":{"primary":"Zelenskyy accuses Russia of 'cowardliness' in latest video address","seo":"Zelenskyy accuses Russia of 'cowardliness' in latest video address","social":"Zelenskyy accuses Russia of 'cowardliness' in latest video address"},"primaryImage":null,"taxonomy":{"primaryChannel":{"id":"rctx38","path":"nbcnews/channel/nebula-blog-rcna23749","taxono